<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Deletion Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .message {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="message">
    <p>Dear {{ name }},</p>
    <p>We regret to inform you that your account in {{ client }} has been deleted due to inactivity for the last 30 days.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact the administrator.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>